Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有誰從一開始就是廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是哪位姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都擁有與愛麗絲相配的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好  天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過不要到這裡來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也有話想要對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我父母來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後他們問  要不要請個人來照料我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實陪床什麼的有沒有還不是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他們兩個卻都是一副很慚愧的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著他們這樣  我就會想到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啊  這全都要怪我啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點用盡我的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不說我也會這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎？就這樣結束生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像是天使你會說出的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是沒有辦法的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我  從剛出生的時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一個廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多呢  你們兩個不用這麼著急哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一幫沒修養到極點的傢伙的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然身為薔薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃東西的時候就應當優雅…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小雛先吃完的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小金先吃完的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要矯正你們的性格的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一下的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是嘈吵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把籽取掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這裡面有多少籽啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒等你開始吃就要天黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真囉嗦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀  給我換一塊小一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫小不點的小不點！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天要給她們點顏色看看的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  的確是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石  你來了的說啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀切了西瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  水銀燈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  再看看情況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有時間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要來看槐老師製作人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參觀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你說過他喜歡人偶的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為總是來店裡面  所以想讓他看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:05:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  最好把頭髮剪短點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  如果能夠有些有趣的事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上燒製好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直冷卻到早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是明天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要燒製這麼長時間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淬火燒製後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會變成這麼小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼小？好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個是個失敗品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…失敗的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也許你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  這樣就沒問題啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫庫  不行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間房子的窗戶和門都用鑰匙鎖住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您仔細看看  是那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？啊！這個是…螞蟻！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  就是螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫庫好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  這種推理對於我薔薇少女中第一的頭腦派金絲雀來說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很輕鬆就可以做出來了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫庫比較厲害哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能安靜的好好看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到純的房間裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！庫庫  危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面  在後面啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}在後面啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  沒錯  我的聲音傳達到他那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}謝謝！謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}時間不多了  請趕快！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個女人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石  都這個時候了你怎麼還在這裡的說啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爺爺吵架了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來問你的想法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會怎麼樣？如果愛麗絲遊戲開始了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  會戰鬥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…你突然間問我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  蒼星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石  你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:09:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你…你要做什麼的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  快停下的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是人偶對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我也要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼被做出來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我在想羅真  你們的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇聖母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子  如果有薔薇聖母的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能救活她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有薔薇聖母的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不過是小事一件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於父親大人的事  我幾乎記不起什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是  包容著我的那溫柔  那溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一切事物中保護我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過肌膚直達心底的思念  溫暖  慈愛的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使一無所有  那裡也有一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得他的樣子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一點點印象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛莓  翠星石還有蒼星石呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們也都和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只記得是「被溫暖的光芒包圍著的人」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這和樣貌是沒有關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的不是樣貌  而是存在的本身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越時光  改變姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人不論在哪個世界裡都是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了製作出愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之中製作出的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是薔薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要製作出完美的少女「愛麗絲」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒有成功而誕生出的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:12:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  羅真對你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對沒能成為愛麗絲的你們是怎麼想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有能夠成為愛麗絲  就讓你們去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在哭泣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:14:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人  在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為無法找到愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去  只會讓父親大人繼續痛苦下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現父親大人的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓愛麗絲遊戲開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  心情相當不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經萬事俱備了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅真對你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對沒能成為愛麗絲的你們  是怎麼想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有沒有做出過和希望中不一樣的人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念相同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平等？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對人偶抱有的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是平等而相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要注入了愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能賦予它們生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛情…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會迷失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論怎樣的孩子都會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道一個叫作「羅真」的人偶師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您認為羅真也有那種愛情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有愛情  就無法製作人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是完美的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  羅真離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下了沒能成為愛麗絲的7個人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使去了很遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛情也會留下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛情是注入在人偶中的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛才是第一個哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還太嫩了點吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和我比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就接受你的挑戰吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和小金比賽吃刨冰的速度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓你幫我們計時吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…我對你們都無話可說了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會頭疼的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:18:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你沒回去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼  蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來打招呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  要成為愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會與你們戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集薔薇聖母
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…為什麼突然說這種話的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來我們就有著戰鬥的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是必然的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見到了…父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人在痛苦著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為無法找到愛麗絲而哭泣著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在做的事  已經離父親大人的理想太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了把父親大人從痛苦中拯救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有讓我們中的一個成為愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…這是你的意願的話  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不願意的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石在想什麼  真紅說什麼  我才不管的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是作為雙胞胎的姐姐的命令的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你離開我  我是絕對不會原諒你的說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快說點…快說點什麼的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…你的答覆吧  翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  這是大家的答覆！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仔細想想  這不是很奇怪嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼親密的姐妹不得不相互戰鬥呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了完美的少女  又有什麼意義呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有哪裡不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有什麼不滿意的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了追求完美而製作出的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了製作出愛麗絲卻未能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為一個人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要實現父親大人的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石！等一下的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼的說啊？為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.07,0:23:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石她…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有她的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.35,0:23:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也沒有辦法說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.00,0:23:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知什麼時候就會和蒼星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.49,0:23:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.22,0:23:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.09,0:24:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  薔薇少女  夢見
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.39,0:24:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旋律宛如夢中所見
